     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZ.D.DE161</b></p><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZ.D.DE161\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 22 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE162\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE162\">DE162</a></td><td>Currently pregnant</td><td>The client is currently pregnant</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE163\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE163\">DE163</a></td><td>Immunocompromised</td><td>The client is known to be immunocompromised</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE200\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE200\">DE200</a></td><td>Severely immunocompromised</td><td>The client is known to be severely immunocompromised</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE164\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE164\">DE164</a></td><td>Exposed to immunosuppressive treatment</td><td>The client is undergoing immunosuppressive treatment or was exposed to immunosuppressive treatment in utero or via breastfeeding.</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE165\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE165\">DE165</a></td><td>Severely immunosuppressed</td><td>The client is known to be severely immunosuppressed</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE187\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE187\">DE187</a></td><td>Immunodeficiency syndromes</td><td>The client has  immunodeficiency syndromes (e.g. HIV/AIDS, known or suspected congenital immunodeficiency, leukaemia, lymphoma or other malignant disease)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE166\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE166\">DE166</a></td><td>History of anaphylactic reactions</td><td>The client is known to have history of anaphylaxis in the past</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE167\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE167\">DE167</a></td><td>Severe allergic reactions</td><td>The client is known to have severe allergic reaction</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE168\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE168\">DE168</a></td><td>Symptomatic HIV infection</td><td>The client is experiencing HIV-related symptoms</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE169\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE169\">DE169</a></td><td>Planning to get pregnant in the next month</td><td>The client's intention or desire is to become pregnant in the next month</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE170\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE170\">DE170</a></td><td>Receiving blood products</td><td>The client is receiving blood or blood-related products as part of a medical treatment.</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE188\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE188\">DE188</a></td><td>Severe acute illness</td><td>The client has a severe acute illness</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE190\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE190\">DE190</a></td><td>TB disease</td><td>The client has been diagnosed with tuberculosis (TB)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE191\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE191\">DE191</a></td><td>Breastfeeding</td><td>The client is currently breastfeeding</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE192\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE192\">DE192</a></td><td>Spina bifida</td><td>The client has spina bifida<