 href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE198\">DE198</a></td><td>Hypersensitivity to vaccine components</td><td>The client has heightened sensitivity or allergic reactions to specific components found in vaccines</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZ.D.DE161-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE199\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE199\">DE199</a></td><td>Taking antibiotics</td><td>The client is currently taking antibiotics to treat certain infections</td></tr></table></div>"
